1
00:00:51,988 --> 00:00:53,188
Mr. Tu.

2
00:00:55,508 --> 00:00:56,707
Why collaborate with Qin Wei

3
00:00:56,707 --> 00:00:58,308
to target Su Yunian?

4
00:01:00,508 --> 00:01:01,548
Mr. Tu.

5
00:01:10,268 --> 00:01:10,908
Mr. Tu,

6
00:01:11,468 --> 00:01:13,188
I was following your instructions

7
00:01:13,347 --> 00:01:15,227
to teach Su Yunian a lesson.

8
00:01:15,552 --> 00:01:17,152
I never meant to actually hurt her.

9
00:01:18,828 --> 00:01:20,548
Let Lin Shen take her back to the hotel,

10
00:01:20,787 --> 00:01:22,628
and let Qin Wei pull her nail out

11
00:01:23,828 --> 00:01:25,947
just to make her leave
Deep In The Bustle?

12
00:01:26,867 --> 00:01:27,988
Yes, Mr. Tu.

13
00:01:27,988 --> 00:01:29,507
That was the only goal.

14
00:01:41,427 --> 00:01:42,067
Mr. Tu,

15
00:01:44,268 --> 00:01:46,427
I did envy her,

16
00:01:47,748 --> 00:01:50,028
because she looked
so much like An Ruoxi.

17
00:01:53,507 --> 00:01:55,268
You were into Feng before.

18
00:02:00,108 --> 00:02:01,628
When did you start liking me?

19
00:02:02,507 --> 00:02:03,787
Mr. Tu.

20
00:02:08,507 --> 00:02:09,227
Tell me.

21
00:02:11,867 --> 00:02:14,027
Did you and Qin Wei kill An Ruoxi?

22
00:02:14,948 --> 00:02:15,587
No!

23
00:02:15,587 --> 00:02:16,608
No, Mr. Tu!

24
00:02:16,608 --> 00:02:18,068
It really wasn't me, Mr. Tu!

25
00:02:27,027 --> 00:02:29,027
Do you know why I killed Yunyan?

26
00:02:30,948 --> 00:02:31,627
Because

27
00:02:32,788 --> 00:02:34,907
she entered Room 999 without permission,

28
00:02:35,027 --> 00:02:36,427
violating your rules.

29
00:02:37,587 --> 00:02:40,068
She came to my room for some documents.

30
00:02:42,788 --> 00:02:44,388
Do you know what documents?

31
00:02:46,147 --> 00:02:47,147
Mr. Tu.

32
00:02:48,707 --> 00:02:49,508
I...

33
00:02:50,027 --> 00:02:50,707
I...

34
00:02:51,027 --> 00:02:52,988
I did tell her at the time

35
00:02:53,268 --> 00:02:55,108
that Ruoxi liked to keep a diary.

36
00:02:58,228 --> 00:02:59,828
Who wanted that diary,

37
00:03:01,747 --> 00:03:03,548
you or Feng?

38
00:03:03,828 --> 00:03:05,668
No! That's not it, Mr. Tu!

39
00:03:07,147 --> 00:03:08,587
Where's Nie Feng?

40
00:03:08,587 --> 00:03:10,828
I-I don't know.

41
00:03:10,828 --> 00:03:11,627
Mr. Tu,

42
00:03:11,627 --> 00:03:12,672
you're sworn brothers.

43
00:03:12,672 --> 00:03:13,788
You're both my bosses.

44
00:03:14,388 --> 00:03:15,427
There's no way

45
00:03:15,747 --> 00:03:17,587
you'd get his location from me.

46
00:03:17,587 --> 00:03:19,427
Truly loyal to the bone.

47
00:03:26,867 --> 00:03:28,668
You previously said

48
00:03:29,027 --> 00:03:31,508
I like playing slaughter games.

49
00:03:32,068 --> 00:03:32,627
No.

50
00:03:32,627 --> 00:03:33,152
Fine.

51
00:03:33,152 --> 00:03:33,828
No.

52
00:03:34,988 --> 00:03:36,108
I'll show you.

53
00:03:36,108 --> 00:03:37,632
Mr. Tu, I did say that,

54
00:03:37,788 --> 00:03:39,548
but it was just banter between girls!

55
00:03:40,108 --> 00:03:41,867
I returned as I have a clear conscience.

56
00:03:42,144 --> 00:03:43,348
If you kill me,

57
00:03:43,467 --> 00:03:44,988
that's just killing the innocent.

58
00:03:49,828 --> 00:03:50,668
Mr. Tu.

59
00:03:54,587 --> 00:03:55,427
Mr. Tu,

60
00:03:56,467 --> 00:03:57,747
kill me.

61
00:03:59,548 --> 00:04:00,948
If you kill me,

62
00:04:01,828 --> 00:04:03,988
Feng won't let you get away with this!

63
00:04:04,907 --> 00:04:05,747
Mr. Tu,

64
00:04:05,747 --> 00:04:06,948
just kill me!

65
00:04:07,467 --> 00:04:08,587
Go ahead and kill me!

66
00:04:09,427 --> 00:04:10,027
Do it!

67
00:04:10,027 --> 00:04:11,187
If you're not afraid of Feng,

68
00:04:11,187 --> 00:04:12,467
go ahead and shoot!

69
00:04:12,988 --> 00:04:14,108
For Feng's sake,

70
00:04:14,467 --> 00:04:15,548
it's worth it.

71
00:04:21,307 --> 00:04:22,148
Fine.

72
00:04:27,267 --> 00:04:28,668
I'll grant your wish.

73
00:04:32,267 --> 00:04:33,148
Okay.

74
00:04:33,440 --> 00:04:36,672
=The Glory Fades=

75
00:04:36,672 --> 00:04:39,424
=Episode 22=
(Betrayal)

76
00:04:43,067 --> 00:04:43,827
Stand up.

77
00:04:44,187 --> 00:04:45,187
Never ask you to kneel.

78
00:04:47,387 --> 00:04:48,747
Regarding Bai Ruxue,

79
00:04:49,028 --> 00:04:49,827
I was wrong.

80
00:04:50,228 --> 00:04:51,228
I should kneel.

81
00:04:52,588 --> 00:04:53,867
Lu only did it for me.

82
00:04:54,387 --> 00:04:55,387
It's all my fault.

83
00:05:01,348 --> 00:05:02,668
You brought her back anyway.

84
00:05:03,187 --> 00:05:04,148
Get up.

85
00:05:05,668 --> 00:05:06,468
Mr. Tu,

86
00:05:07,827 --> 00:05:08,827
about this matter,

87
00:05:09,427 --> 00:05:10,988
I need to explain clearly.

88
00:05:11,387 --> 00:05:11,908
I...

89
00:05:13,148 --> 00:05:13,747
Okay.

90
00:05:14,387 --> 00:05:15,148
Go ahead.

91
00:05:15,747 --> 00:05:16,548
I'm listening.

92
00:05:28,827 --> 00:05:29,908
Bai Ruxue and I

93
00:05:30,947 --> 00:05:31,827
are townsfolk

94
00:05:32,627 --> 00:05:33,588
with the surname Bai.

95
00:05:35,348 --> 00:05:36,548
We know each other for years.

96
00:05:38,187 --> 00:05:40,028
She once took grave injuries saving me.

97
00:05:40,747 --> 00:05:41,536
That's why

98
00:05:41,536 --> 00:05:43,148
I've treated her like my own sister.

99
00:05:43,548 --> 00:05:44,668
I owe her.

100
00:05:51,468 --> 00:05:52,228
Alright.

101
00:05:53,427 --> 00:05:54,228
Bai Manni,

102
00:05:55,668 --> 00:05:56,588
that explanation holds.

103
00:05:57,827 --> 00:05:58,627
But,

104
00:06:00,067 --> 00:06:01,468
I have a question for you.

105
00:06:04,668 --> 00:06:05,867
Then what am I?

106
00:06:10,827 --> 00:06:11,747
To you,

107
00:06:12,627 --> 00:06:13,668
what am I?

108
00:06:15,988 --> 00:06:17,228
You're my boss.

109
00:06:17,548 --> 00:06:18,348
Also...

110
00:06:21,067 --> 00:06:21,947
What else?

111
00:06:24,708 --> 00:06:26,028
Jiasheng.

112
00:06:32,468 --> 00:06:33,468
Traitor!

113
00:06:48,788 --> 00:06:49,588
Lu.

114
00:06:50,668 --> 00:06:51,307
Lu,

115
00:06:51,468 --> 00:06:53,028
Mr. Tu had his men outside

116
00:06:53,028 --> 00:06:53,947
surround the top floor.

117
00:06:54,468 --> 00:06:55,468
Didn't dare to barge in.

118
00:06:55,867 --> 00:06:57,348
Send all security to the top floor.

119
00:06:57,468 --> 00:06:58,067
No one enters

120
00:06:58,067 --> 00:06:58,668
or leaves

121
00:06:58,668 --> 00:06:59,427
without my say-so.

122
00:06:59,427 --> 00:06:59,947
Understood.

123
00:08:19,827 --> 00:08:20,627
Bai Manni,

124
00:08:22,148 --> 00:08:23,788
for the sake of old times,

125
00:08:25,228 --> 00:08:26,668
I won't pursue other matters.

126
00:08:27,988 --> 00:08:29,067
But tell me.

127
00:08:30,627 --> 00:08:31,668
Do you really think

128
00:08:33,067 --> 00:08:35,067
Feng will offer you a brighter future?

129
00:08:36,228 --> 00:08:37,028
No.

130
00:08:39,027 --> 00:08:40,308
Never.

131
00:08:40,588 --> 00:08:42,147
We've worked together all these years.

132
00:08:42,547 --> 00:08:43,387
Don't you know

133
00:08:43,387 --> 00:08:44,468
my loyalty to you?

134
00:08:54,468 --> 00:08:56,068
If it hadn't been for Qin Wei,

135
00:08:56,428 --> 00:08:57,308
you and I...

136
00:09:02,267 --> 00:09:04,348
Although you later had An Ruoxi.

137
00:09:06,387 --> 00:09:07,387
I was envious,

138
00:09:09,468 --> 00:09:10,267
but honestly,

139
00:09:12,147 --> 00:09:13,468
as long as you're happy,

140
00:09:14,188 --> 00:09:15,428
that's what matters most.

141
00:09:21,856 --> 00:09:23,040
But what about you?

142
00:09:25,188 --> 00:09:27,387
Have you ever thought about me,
even a little?

143
00:09:29,547 --> 00:09:30,588
Do you know how I lived

144
00:09:30,588 --> 00:09:32,027
through the days when I felt

145
00:09:32,027 --> 00:09:32,988
I'd completely lost you?

146
00:09:32,988 --> 00:09:34,188
Do you know?

147
00:09:42,867 --> 00:09:44,348
I told myself,

148
00:09:46,828 --> 00:09:49,027
since I couldn't be the woman
in your arms,

149
00:09:50,387 --> 00:09:52,027
I'd give my all

150
00:09:53,387 --> 00:09:55,308
to be your right hand.

151
00:10:03,228 --> 00:10:03,828
Manni,

152
00:10:07,027 --> 00:10:08,428
thank you for all these years

153
00:10:09,387 --> 00:10:10,627
for following me and doing

154
00:10:12,228 --> 00:10:13,068
so much for me.

155
00:10:14,468 --> 00:10:15,507
I remember it all.

156
00:10:17,787 --> 00:10:18,507
But,

157
00:10:20,027 --> 00:10:22,027
this can't justify you helping Bai Ruxue

158
00:10:22,228 --> 00:10:24,068
or Nie Feng behind her.

159
00:10:24,867 --> 00:10:25,667
Do you understand?

160
00:10:26,828 --> 00:10:27,428
Mr. Tu,

161
00:10:29,267 --> 00:10:31,027
you keep calling him by his full name,

162
00:10:32,428 --> 00:10:34,627
so there's a problem between you.

163
00:10:34,627 --> 00:10:35,867
But to me,

164
00:10:36,988 --> 00:10:38,907
you two have always been harmonious.

165
00:10:38,907 --> 00:10:39,627
So,

166
00:10:41,147 --> 00:10:41,948
I truly don't

167
00:10:42,688 --> 00:10:44,428
understand your words.

168
00:10:51,188 --> 00:10:51,907
Is that so?

169
00:10:53,907 --> 00:10:55,027
You still think

170
00:10:56,667 --> 00:10:57,627
he and I

171
00:11:00,147 --> 00:11:01,867
are still who we were?

172
00:11:02,188 --> 00:11:03,267
(Hello, Feng.)

173
00:11:03,787 --> 00:11:05,387
I'll say it again.

174
00:11:05,747 --> 00:11:06,667
Call me

175
00:11:07,147 --> 00:11:08,027
Boss.

176
00:11:09,068 --> 00:11:10,027
Yes, Boss.

177
00:11:10,228 --> 00:11:11,747
That's more like it.

178
00:11:12,867 --> 00:11:15,027
Unless in front of Lu and the others,

179
00:11:16,027 --> 00:11:18,787
always use that title.

180
00:11:20,867 --> 00:11:22,708
'Boss.'

181
00:11:24,228 --> 00:11:25,147
Yes, Boss.

182
00:11:25,147 --> 00:11:25,948
I'm listening.

183
00:11:52,387 --> 00:11:53,108
Manni,

184
00:11:55,588 --> 00:11:58,027
for someone with no blood ties,

185
00:12:00,907 --> 00:12:01,907
you betrayed me.

186
00:12:05,228 --> 00:12:06,348
I'm truly disappointed.

187
00:12:09,507 --> 00:12:10,507
Disappointed?

188
00:12:15,027 --> 00:12:16,188
Disappointed?

189
00:12:21,027 --> 00:12:22,988
Well, let disappointed be.

190
00:12:25,428 --> 00:12:26,627
I've tasted many times

191
00:12:26,787 --> 00:12:28,588
the taste of disappointment.

192
00:12:33,547 --> 00:12:34,787
I've disappointed you?

193
00:12:38,027 --> 00:12:38,988
Tell me.

194
00:12:39,267 --> 00:12:40,867
Where have I disappointed you?

195
00:12:40,867 --> 00:12:42,228
Haven't you?

196
00:12:45,948 --> 00:12:48,027
Mr. Tu, you don't even dare admit it?

197
00:12:49,747 --> 00:12:51,627
Don't you know what you

198
00:12:51,627 --> 00:12:53,188
once meant to me?

199
00:12:56,468 --> 00:12:57,468
Have you forgotten

200
00:12:58,507 --> 00:13:01,228
what happened back then?

201
00:13:08,907 --> 00:13:09,907
What happened?

202
00:13:10,988 --> 00:13:11,988
This was an accident.

203
00:13:12,828 --> 00:13:14,348
We're discussing something.

204
00:13:15,547 --> 00:13:16,667
Go out first.

205
00:13:17,468 --> 00:13:18,387
Stand up!

206
00:13:18,828 --> 00:13:20,547
At Deep In The Bustle,
we kneel to no one.

207
00:13:22,308 --> 00:13:23,108
Go!

208
00:13:31,068 --> 00:13:33,228
We must clear things up today,

209
00:13:33,667 --> 00:13:35,948
or no one leaves Room 999.

210
00:13:39,907 --> 00:13:40,667
I'm leaving then.

211
00:13:40,667 --> 00:13:42,188
How do you plan to stop me?

212
00:13:43,867 --> 00:13:45,348
I've managed security these years.

213
00:13:46,787 --> 00:13:48,188
I'm taking Manni away now.

214
00:13:49,027 --> 00:13:51,228
I'll show you no one
at Deep In The Bustle

215
00:13:51,627 --> 00:13:53,547
dares to stop me.

216
00:13:53,588 --> 00:13:55,867
Do you even see me as your brother?

217
00:13:57,667 --> 00:13:58,588
Brother?

218
00:13:59,468 --> 00:14:01,228
You planted spies in my security team

219
00:14:02,048 --> 00:14:03,468
and secretly bought off my father's

220
00:14:03,468 --> 00:14:05,468
moles in the military and police.

221
00:14:06,188 --> 00:14:07,387
This is what a brother does?

222
00:14:08,428 --> 00:14:09,867
I let my guard down around you,

223
00:14:11,228 --> 00:14:12,387
but I'm not stupid.

224
00:14:30,667 --> 00:14:32,027
How dare you accuse me?

225
00:14:35,068 --> 00:14:36,064
You think I don't know

226
00:14:36,064 --> 00:14:37,988
what you and Nie Feng did
behind my back?

227
00:14:40,547 --> 00:14:41,667
You're sidelining me.

228
00:14:42,267 --> 00:14:44,867
Just because I lack a powerful father,

229
00:14:44,867 --> 00:14:47,027
I handle all the dirty work.

230
00:14:47,188 --> 00:14:49,387
Have you ever treated me as family?

231
00:15:01,988 --> 00:15:02,787
All these years,

232
00:15:05,188 --> 00:15:07,387
have I ever refused you once?

233
00:15:13,627 --> 00:15:15,387
I won't get involved with you with Feng,

234
00:15:17,787 --> 00:15:19,387
but Manni is coming with me.

235
00:15:27,428 --> 00:15:28,747
What if I forbid it?

236
00:15:40,387 --> 00:15:42,428
Please don't make me do this.

237
00:15:47,147 --> 00:15:48,667
You're pointing a gun at me?

238
00:15:49,627 --> 00:15:50,867
I'm your brother.

239
00:15:53,627 --> 00:15:55,068
Please don't.

240
00:15:55,867 --> 00:15:56,988
What are you doing?

241
00:16:15,668 --> 00:16:19,342
♪If the heart can't hear the sorrow♪

242
00:16:19,641 --> 00:16:22,832
♪It only makes everything look so fake♪

243
00:16:24,664 --> 00:16:28,285
♪Your eyes resemble hers too much♪

244
00:16:28,834 --> 00:16:31,633
♪Who makes me forget whom♪

245
00:16:33,104 --> 00:16:36,834
♪The warmth in my heart is fading♪

246
00:16:37,058 --> 00:16:40,555
♪Every glance feels like atonement♪

247
00:16:41,954 --> 00:16:45,641
♪Ambiguity hidden in the night breeze♪

248
00:16:46,279 --> 00:16:51,394
♪Blows away the chance to explain♪

249
00:16:52,098 --> 00:16:56,232
♪I feel guilty♪

250
00:16:56,802 --> 00:17:00,546
♪I'll have no regrets
even I leave quietly♪

251
00:17:01,410 --> 00:17:04,853
♪Even in tears♪

252
00:17:05,602 --> 00:17:09,516
♪It doesn't matter♪

253
00:17:09,698 --> 00:17:13,521
♪We embrace in dreams♪

254
00:17:14,370 --> 00:17:17,808
♪I let down all my defenses♪

255
00:17:19,042 --> 00:17:22,405
♪Though the story has its end♪

256
00:17:23,170 --> 00:17:31,522
♪I'll journey with you all my life♪
